  "detailed_description": "Step into a world where rhythm meets precision in this adrenaline-pumping VR game. Pulsar is an electrifying fusion of music, lasers, and moving targets that promises an immersive gaming experience like no other.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Pulsar:</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/c74d6b45a4954508a6d4a29d8f050d73.avif?t=1745610745\" width=600 height=78 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/3e6d6ab1e43a225916d4ccd333ce43f7.poster.avif?t=1745610745\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/3e6d6ab1e43a225916d4ccd333ce43f7.webm?t=1745610745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/3e6d6ab1e43a225916d4ccd333ce43f7.mp4?t=1745610745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay that Dances to Your Beat:</h2>Prepare to be enthralled as you take center stage in this high-octane virtual reality extravaganza. Your mission? To shoot down moving targets with laser precision while grooving to the music of your choice. The game syncs seamlessly with your desktop music library, allowing you to set the perfect soundtrack to your action-packed adventure. Feel the rhythm pulse through your veins as you lock onto targets and let loose with your laser blasters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/787a607aa0f4638b1a90b48b14bbe01d.poster.avif?t=1745610745\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/787a607aa0f4638b1a90b48b14bbe01d.webm?t=1745610745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/787a607aa0f4638b1a90b48b14bbe01d.mp4?t=1745610745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br>BYOM: Bring Your Own Music, using the built in file browser select your favourite music and the game will analyze the waveform of the track and procedurally generates the beats in line with the music., No mods needed, no concerns about music licences expiring in the future.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/8f278f4c79dfc2f1a03f38349a0a936c.avif?t=1745610745\" width=600 height=78 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626030/extras/3b94088ac2569e7468c0bf36d35b8f3b.avif?t=1745610745\" width=600 height=78 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >See also:</h2>",
